### open-insurance-transmissor-reference — REST Client requests

@host = http://localhost:8083

### 1) Lista apólices do CPF seed 1 (paginada)

GET {{host}}/open-insurance/insurance-policies/v1/policies?documentType=CPF&document=12345678901&page=1&page-size=10

> {% client.global.set("policyId", response.body.data[0].policyId); %}

### 2) Detalhe da primeira apólice retornada

GET {{host}}/open-insurance/insurance-policies/v1/policies/{{policyId}}

### 3) Lista de outro CPF seed (categoria diferente)

GET {{host}}/open-insurance/insurance-policies/v1/policies?documentType=CPF&document=98765432109&page=1&page-size=5

### 4) Apólice inexistente — esperado 404 POLICY_NOT_FOUND

GET {{host}}/open-insurance/insurance-policies/v1/policies/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 5) Health check

GET {{host}}/actuator/health
